title: Whose Souls? Demon's Souls
description: The boys brave the fetid swamps and fiery dragons of the prettiest dang PS5 game around, Demon's Souls. Will they survive the Valley of Defilement? Will they find a lovely two bedroom in the Tower of Latria? Only one way to find out!
author: thebestiesbizemail@gmail.com (The Besties)
